/" rel="tag">Francesca Micarelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/francesco-verna/" rel="tag">Francesco Verna</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/franco-zeffirelli/" rel="tag">Franco Zeffirelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/georges-bizet/" rel="tag">Georges Bizet</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/henrik-nanasi/" rel="tag">Henrik Nanasi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/irina-lungu/" rel="tag">irina lungu</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lucia-real/" rel="tag">Lucia Real</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/paolo-antognetti/" rel="tag">Paolo Antognetti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/seung-pil-choi/" rel="tag">Seung Pil Choi</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Anna Anni, Arena di Verona 2014, Arena Opera Festival 2014, Carlo Ventre, Carlos Alvarez, Carmen, Cristina Melis, Ekaterina Semenchuk, El Camborio, Federico Longhi, Francesca Micarelli, Francesco Verna, Franco Zeffirelli, Georges Bizet, Henrik Nanasi, irina lungu, Lucia Real, Opera lirica, Paolo Antognetti, Seung Pil Choi"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/6699ffadacad646736fb668601ae4e49" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/soundcloud-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="redazioneGBopera" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="redazione GBopera"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/redazionegbopera/">View all articles by redazioneGBopera</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/06/un-ballo-in-maschera-allarena-di-verona/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> &#8220;Un ballo in maschera&#8221; all&#8217;Arena di Verona</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/06/verona-arena-opera-festival-2014carmen-english-review/" rel="next">Verona, Arena Opera Festival 2014:&#8221;Carmen&#8221; (english review) <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2014/06/verona-arena-opera-festivalcarmen/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sarà pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required='true' required='required' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="ema